</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>lengths</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The lengths of the words of each tape (size of lengths == the levels of <computeroutput>nft</computeroutput>) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>std::optional&lt;std::vector&lt;Word&gt;&gt; Either the resulting words of tapes, or std::nullopt if such words of specific lengths do not exist </para>
